^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Even with weak 5-5-2-1 you can bid 2@C (Crawling Stayman) and over a 2@D response bid 2@H and follow as above. If you don't want to bother to play Crawling Stayman, then simply transfer to your better major, and pass when opener accepts the transfer. This works out fine usually. BTW, 5-2 fit plays better than the 4-4 fit. And a 5-3 fit almost always plays better than a 4-4 fit.|
